                    android:padding="5dp"
                    android:text="KetekMall may delay, suspend or cancel any Payment in case Seller breaches any term of the      Agreement or Customer Agreement and any Payment made to Seller will not in any way be     considered as a waiver of KetekMall’s rights. " />

